Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:04.78,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:10.90,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:17.09,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:23.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:26.91,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:29.96,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:36.49,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:45.96,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:52.26,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.46,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:03:01.81,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:07.09,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 拉克丝 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的朋友哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗哈罗 你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要和你握手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人少来厚颜无耻地套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你对我好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我你的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是地球军舰艇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位45.01A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成航向修正
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎60%功率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 跟先遣队一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾在船上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经把名单发过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么提问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:15.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}消失的光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是奥布的环境好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹能和家里取得联系了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾这是在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去见谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做面膜 没见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 算了不跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西你随身带？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸要和先遣队一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得打理打理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大西洋联邦事务次官的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太蓬头垢面的有损爸爸形象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说好久没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然得打扮漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 没地方做头发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 非常时期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰队将按预定时间抵达交汇点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会合后 大天使号将编入本舰队指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往与大部队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了 祝你们平安抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大西洋联邦事务次官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治·阿尔斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先就营救平民的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我向你们表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常高兴地发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获救人员清单上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小女芙蕾·阿尔斯塔的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到甚是惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能让我见她一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事务次官阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会合后马上可以相见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾的爸爸还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 来看看你在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根据偏移值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也调整下其他参数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过也没必要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 做吧做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大部队会合前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些还是你的活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的话可以志愿留下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:26.80,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}静静的夜里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:39.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}等你拾回忘却的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:56.07,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}那件事已过好久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:07:05.36,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}记忆也磨去了棱角
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:15.86,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}在流星划落的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:27.21,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}祈祷你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:34.46,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}即便天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:41.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}终会相见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是地球军舰队的预测航线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格尼和珀尔的队伍可能要迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是为长腿运送补给的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就此放过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要进攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们首先是军人 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕肩负搜寻拉克丝小姐的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达发现三艘船体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护卫舰 蒙哥马利 巴纳德 劳乌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干扰！范围覆盖整个宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长的直觉从没错过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 让我们见识下这东西的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是为长腿运送补给的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就此放过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:09:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为保护我们的家园而战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果安全须靠武力去赢取
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只有一战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也说讨厌战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么要毁了赫利奥波利斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动堡垒 紧急出动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹及反光束爆雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全门装填
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热源接近 机动战士4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么被人跟踪还不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰首下沉 俯角30
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左转向 仰角20
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电告大天使号迅速撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下 你认为我们能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会合的话 来这里有何意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船如果被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就更加没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热传感器发现 前方似有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是先遣队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙哥马利号来电
